{
  "page": "Dagon's Feast",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>Dagon's Feast</b></i> is an <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> longship in the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Fleet\" title=\"Iron Fleet\">Iron Fleet</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It is presumably named after Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Dagon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Dagon Greyjoy\">Dagon Greyjoy</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dagon%27s_Feast&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dagon%27s_Feast&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><i>Dagon's</i> Feast accompanies the rest of the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Fleet\" title=\"Iron Fleet\">Iron Fleet</a> when they sail for <a href=\"/index.php/Slaver%27s_Bay\" title=\"Slaver&#39;s Bay\">Slaver's Bay</a>. It sinks along with <i><a href=\"/index.php/Red_Tide\" title=\"Red Tide\">Red Tide</a></i> when both ships crash into one another during a storm on the voyage.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dagon%27s_Feast&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_56\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 56\">Chapter 56</a>, The Iron Suitor.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403102625\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.024 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.048 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 255/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8597/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 792/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 44/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 812/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.51 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   42.555      1 -total\n 80.56%   34.284      1 Template:Italic_title\n 15.08%    6.418      2 Template:Ref\n 10.31%    4.389      2 Template:Ref/core\n  3.76%    1.599      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaf